.SH "SECURITY"
.PP
\fBarping\fR
requires CAP_NET_RAW capability to be executed\&. It is not recommended to be used as set\-uid root, because it allows user to modify ARP caches of neighbour hosts\&.
.SH "AVAILABILITY"
.PP
\fBarping\fR
is part of
\fIiputils\fR
package\&.
